<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'pages', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 class="service display-4 text-center">Our Services !!</h1><br>
  <p class="lead text-center">Our restaurant tries to provide the best services to its customers. They include services from the restaurant to your doorsteps.</p>
  <hr class="my-4">
  <h4 class="text-center">Come as a Guest Go as a Friend</h4><br>
  <center>
    <a class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" href="/orders/new" role="button"><%=fa_icon "cart-arrow-down"%>
      Order Now</a>
    <a class="btn btn-warning btn-sm" href="/books/new" role="button"><%=fa_icon "bookmark"%>
      Book Table</a>
    <hr>
    <h5 class="text-center">Follow Us</h5><br>
    <a class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm" href="https://www.facebook.com/Sankhalifa.33" target="_blank" role="button">
      <%=fa_icon "facebook"%>
      Facebook »</a>
    <a class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm" href="https://www.instagram.com/_sankalpa_neupane/?hl=en/" target="_blank" role="button">
      <%=fa_icon "instagram"%>
      Instagram »</a>
  </center>
</div>

<div class="container my-1">
  <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
        <h2 class="mb-0">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-center text-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
            Environment
          </button>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
        <div class="card-body">
          We have very peaceful environment for eating. The order is super fast so, you dont have to wait for too long. There is a separate room for smokers. Therefore, there is no problem for those of you who dont like the smoke of a ciggarate. We have
          separate place for celebrations and parties. Hence there is no disturbance. Proper sanitation is maintained. Air conditioning and free wifi are available. Waiters are very friendly. And the stunning view of the Lake will add more taste to your food.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
        <h2 class="mb-0">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-center text-primary collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
            Delivery System
          </button>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
        <div class="card-body">
          Currently, we have like 20 delivery men actively working for the delivery services which makes the delivery process super fast. Just order the food and our men will be at your doorsteps at no time. We take Rs 100 extra for the service but its is
          nothing as compared to the service we provide. You can reserve a table for birthday celebrations, parties, anniversaries and other events for certain number of people for certain time.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
        <h2 class="mb-0">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-center text-info collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
            Immediate Problem Fixing
          </button>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
        <div class="card-body">
          If our customers find any problems regarding our services, they can report us through the contacts or report us directly in the restuarant or telephone us. We try to remove those problems immediately and make sure these doesn't occur in the future.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
